## Part 4 — Community and Monetization

### Platform — Fourthwall

Everything runs through Fourthwall — memberships, merch, and the storefront. One platform, one brand experience, one URL. Fourthwall is fully white-label, has native Twitch gifting integration, zero platform fee on physical products, and saves roughly $3,500 per year versus Patreon at 500 members. Discord handles community; Signal handles the inner circle.

### Membership Tiers

#### Scrivener — $7.77/month
*The community tier. The room where you don't have to shrink.*

- Exclusive Discord channels with behind-the-scenes worldbuilding and process
- Early access to all YouTube videos
- Name displayed during the Outside Inn warmup on every stream
- Septimal loyalty badges on a base-7 cycle (month 1, 7, 14, etc.)
- 7% merch discount
- Community polls on gaming stream games and worldbuilding topics

The first 777 Scriveners receive a permanent numbered Founding Scrivener badge. Lower numbers are earlier. Once all 777 are claimed, they are gone.

#### Keeper — $21.21/month
*The inner circle. Everything above, plus:*

- Monthly patron-only livestream — 45 to 60 minutes, AMA-style, the conversation not the performance
- Signal group thread — lives on their phone, the back table at the inn
- Name in video credits
- Royalty-free use of Outside Inn music tracks in their own content
- Exclusive merch drops announced in Signal first
- 14% merch discount
- Writing review after 7 consecutive months — up to one chapter, privately or on stream, their choice

The first 77 Keepers receive a permanent numbered Founding Keeper badge. Once 77 are claimed, they are gone.

### The Pricing

$7.77 and $21.21. Base-7 runs through the entire fantasy world — the septimal numeral system, the creation myths, the cosmology. The prices carry that DNA. $7.77 is elevated enough to not feel like a tip jar. $21.21 is a real commitment that justifies real access. Scriveners get 7% merch discount. Keepers get 14%. The sevens are in the details.

### Merch — Two Lines, One Store

| Product | Price | Est. Margin |
|---|---|---|
| Classic Mousepad (EIW or Outside Inn) | $21.21 | ~53% |
| Gaming Mousepad (EIW or Outside Inn) | $28.28 | ~57% |
| Deskmat 15.5" x 31.5" (EIW or Outside Inn) | $49.49 | ~70% |
| Poster 18x24 unframed (EIW or Outside Inn) | $21.21 | ~50% |
