The EIW line is black and white, painterly, literary. The Outside Inn line is warm pixel art, lo-fi atmosphere. Two visual languages under one store. No wordmarks. Elevated enough that someone would buy it without knowing the brand. The deskmat is the hero product at roughly 70% margin.

### Community Architecture

**Discord — The Outside Inn.** Free and open to anyone. Tier-gated channels unlock for Scriveners and Keepers via Fourthwall's Discord integration. The open Discord is the lobby. The gated channels are the real room.

**Signal — The Back Table.** Keepers only. Not Discord — lives on their phone. Members talk to each other. Late-night paragraph screenshots, real-time thoughts, the stuff too small for a post but too personal for Discord.

